  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet to let it air and boil half a kettle</p><p>Rinse your <strong>sushi rice</strong> in a sieve under <strong>cold running water</strong> for 30 secs (use your hands to really wash the grains!), then set aside to drain fully</p><p>Add the <strong>drained rice</strong> with 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> to a pot with a lid and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1586266001040-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1586266001040-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1586266001040-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1586266001040-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1586266001040-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is boiling, reduce the heat to low until very gently bubbling and cook, covered, for 15 min</p><p>After 15 min, remove the pot from the heat and keep covered for a further 10 min before serving</p><p>Tip: Don't peek! Keep the lid on the whole time to get fluffy and sticky rice!</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1586266005024-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1586266005024-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1586266005024-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1586266005024-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1586266005024-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your<strong> chicken breast portion[s] </strong>and cook for 3 min on each side</p><p>Once the chicken has browned, add 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>water</strong> to the pan and cover with a lid</p><p>Cook for 12-15 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1596631782224-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1596631782224-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1596631782224-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
