          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1596631782224-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong>, then combine the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> (not a big garlic fan? Try using less!), <strong>tahini</strong>, <strong>mayo</strong>, and <strong>rice vinegar</strong> in a large bowl</p><p>Season with <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>Japanese-style dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1596631798037-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1596631798037-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1596631798037-x700.jpg",
