          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1596631798037-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1596631798037-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top, tail, peel and grate your<strong> carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>sugar snap peas</strong> in half lengthways</p><p>Slice your <strong>apple[s]</strong> finely, discard the core then chop into matchsticks</p><p>Add the <strong>grated carrot</strong>, <strong>apple matchsticks</strong> and <strong>halved</strong> <strong>sugar snap peas</strong> to the Japanese-style dressing and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>Japanese-style slaw</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1596631815103-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1596631815103-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1596631815103-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1596631815103-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1596631815103-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>cornflour</strong> with your <strong>soy sauce</strong> and <strong>honey</strong> in a small bowl – this is your <strong>soy glaze</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/spicy-soy-sauce-1596631925364-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/spicy-soy-sauce-1596631925364-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/spicy-soy-sauce-1596631925364-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/spicy-soy-sauce-1596631925364-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/spicy-soy-sauce-1596631925364-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked, add the <strong>soy glaze </strong>to the pan and cook for 2-3 min further, stirring occasionally, until the sauce has thickened and the chicken is fully coated</p><p>Transfer the <strong>soy-glazed chicken</strong> to a clean board and slice finely</p><p>Slice your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> finely</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1586266026556-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1586266026556-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1586266026556-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1586266026556-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1586266026556-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>sliced soy-glazed chicken</strong> over the <strong>sticky sushi rice</strong> with the <strong>Japanese-style slaw</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle any <strong>remaining soy glaze </strong>from the pan over the chicken and garnish with the <strong>sliced red chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
